      "span_text": "A sample size of 108 patients per treatment group was estimated to provide 90% power to determine non-inferiority of methoxyflurane versus SAT for the primary outcome measure, assuming a non-inferiority margin of 1.0, a standard deviation of 2.5 [CITATION_1] and a significance level of 0.05."
